{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/projects/collecting.design/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"d1e449e8-ba49-568f-99a8-fece3c3d7ba9","excerpt":"最初诞生这个想法是在去年。我们设计团队每周都会开一个分享会，大家把自己最近看到的好网站、新玩意儿分享出来，一起获取灵感扩宽视野。 当时我们一起维护了一个 Wiki…","html":"<p>最初诞生这个想法是在去年。我们设计团队每周都会开一个分享会，大家把自己最近看到的好网站、新玩意儿分享出来，一起获取灵感扩宽视野。</p>\n<p>当时我们一起维护了一个 Wiki，会及时把自己分享的内容放到里面。但随着分享内容增多，搜索特定条目就变得困难，不方便查阅。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/e7ec1/15640573668819.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"用 Wiki 管理设计分享\"\n        title=\"用 Wiki 管理设计分享\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/c08c5/15640573668819.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/0913d/15640573668819.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/cb69c/15640573668819.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/c08c5/15640573668819.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/6a068/15640573668819.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/eea4a/15640573668819.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/3c8fda2620b42372f63f6d6026dde7d6/e7ec1/15640573668819.jpg 1378w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>当时我就产生了一个想法：<strong>如果我们能够有一个集中管理的地方就好了，它有点像几个人一起维护的一个设计导航。</strong>随后几天里我开始构思它的功能，并做了一个设计效果图，但我没有急于马上实现。</p>\n<h2>验证想法</h2>\n<p>为了验证这个想法的需求量有多大，我做了一个<a href=\"https://collecting.design/tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">落地页</a>，并放了一个邮箱订阅提醒的按钮，想看看有多少人会对这个产品感兴趣。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/de062/15640578844620.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"DesignCollecting 落地页\"\n        title=\"DesignCollecting 落地页\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/c08c5/15640578844620.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/0913d/15640578844620.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/cb69c/15640578844620.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/c08c5/15640578844620.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/6a068/15640578844620.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/eea4a/15640578844620.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/7cee6c4379bd65410d15a442b60068eb/de062/15640578844620.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>当时我在自己的公众号和即刻账号上进行了小范围宣传，随后断断续续收到了九十多个订阅，很多人订阅时还留言给了一些建议请求。这时候我才坚定了要把它实现的想法，不过在后来我又重新思考了一下它的功能。</p>\n<h2>重新思考实现</h2>\n<p>最开始的想法是把它作为一个团队的工具，但是仔细想了想这样便限制了它的使用场景，只局限在了设计分享会。于是，我把“团队”的定义扩大：<strong>任何人都可以用它收集自己喜欢的网站，也可以把自己的收集分享给所有人</strong>。</p>\n<p>最终我把它的主要功能定位在收集、管理和分享设计灵感。首先，每个人都可以收集自己喜欢的设计网站，只需要填写一个链接，就能够自动解析出网站内容，存到自己的收集中。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/f145d/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.12500000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"收集一个网址\"\n        title=\"收集一个网址\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/c08c5/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/0913d/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/cb69c/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/c08c5/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/6a068/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/eea4a/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/31db369156a483c01abb115937054422/f145d/WX20190725-204355%402x.jpg 2320w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这样，每个人就都有了一个专属于自己的设计导航，还可以随时增加或更新。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/de062/15640591106409.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"设计导航\"\n        title=\"设计导航\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/c08c5/15640591106409.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/0913d/15640591106409.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/cb69c/15640591106409.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/c08c5/15640591106409.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/6a068/15640591106409.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/eea4a/15640591106409.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/25de9fff1d2ec396cf91ff25ba2b4a8c/de062/15640591106409.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>其次，为了方便查找，收集的卡片还可以使用分类管理。这样，就能保证自己收集的设计灵感井井有条。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/de062/15640590138520.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"分类管理设计灵感\"\n        title=\"分类管理设计灵感\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/c08c5/15640590138520.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/0913d/15640590138520.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/cb69c/15640590138520.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/c08c5/15640590138520.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/6a068/15640590138520.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/eea4a/15640590138520.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/14139c2a6a17e9948bf45b8fd8691230/de062/15640590138520.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>最后，我们还可以把自己收集的设计灵感分享到首页，这样其他用户打开首页也能看到这张卡片啦。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/65072/15640593411567.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"分享设计灵感\"\n        title=\"分享设计灵感\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/c08c5/15640593411567.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/0913d/15640593411567.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/cb69c/15640593411567.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/c08c5/15640593411567.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/bd26c4cde659478450c626dfe0575e59/65072/15640593411567.jpg 830w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>当我在首页看到了别人分享的设计灵感时，我还可以把它采集到自己的收集中。这样经过分享、采集，就形成了一个正向循环，相当于所有的用户在一起是一个“团队”，我们互相交换设计灵感。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/ba98a/15640596552533.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"收集设计灵感\"\n        title=\"收集设计灵感\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/c08c5/15640596552533.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/0913d/15640596552533.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/cb69c/15640596552533.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/c08c5/15640596552533.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/6a068/15640596552533.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/eea4a/15640596552533.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/4942a0a2d668a0722bb8c44c1d4ddc0a/ba98a/15640596552533.jpg 1484w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>经过半年的打磨，<a href=\"https://collecting.design\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DesignCollecting</a> 终于上线了。如果你正好有这样的需求，可以去尝试一下。它还不够完美，所以我留了一个反馈入口（登录后左侧菜单中），有任何问题、建议你都可以去那里告诉我。</p>\n<p>我希望有更多设计师能够用它收集灵感，也向这个世界分享和交换灵感。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"想收集设计相关的网址？试试我做的这个网页工具","date":"2019/07/25","description":"收集、管理、分享你的设计灵感。","color":"#FFF","cover":"collecting.design.jpg","demo":"https://collecting.design","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/collecting.design/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/designtools/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"我做了个设计工具集，帮你找到最合适的设计工具"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tutorial/a-list-for-designers-portfolio-tools/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"写给设计师的作品集网站搭建指南"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}